 patterns conducive to aligned vector operations and the\nimplementation of hybrid parallelism, using MPI and OMP. Gamera is designed to\nbe a portable and easy-to-use code that implements multi-dimensional MHD\nsimulations in arbitrary non-orthogonal curvilinear geometries on modern\nsupercomputer architectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Oct 2018 13:16:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 19:40:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
